66.1	The_Pursuit_of_Happyness	The Pursuit of Happyness	Pursuit of Happyness is a 2006 American biographical drama film based on Chris Gardner's nearly one-year struggle with homelessness. Directed by Gabriele Muccino, the film features Will Smith as Gardner, an on-and-off-homeless salesman-turned stockbroker. Smith's son Jaden Smith co-stars, making his film debut as Gardner's son Christopher Jr.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/81/Poster-pursuithappyness.jpg/220px-Poster-pursuithappyness.jpg
